snippet.textDisplay:
well sung and composed ..
here i really want to appreciate Hina for coming on stage with dupatta on head.. dont think me backward or conservative and i m certainly not against of those ladies who put on western clothes etc ... i just mean to say this Coke Studio is such a huge platform now to show the world our own culture and elegance and Grace.. 
"maghrabi tau sab ban saktay hain.. maza tau tab hai jab hum apni mashriqi rawayat ko foqiyat daitay hue maghrib ko taskheer karain...  :) "

and the funny Indo-Pak love hatred relationship and comments beneath every coke studio song make me wonder that we are actually siblings , indeed there are some differences in opinions and ideologies,,but we share the same sentiments , wishlists and passion for music..

peace to all..  <3
